data.description: Beautifully rehabbed in 2023, this 3 Bed 2 Bath home offers refinished hardwood floors throughout. New kitchen cabinets, countertops, stainless steel appliances, with a classy backsplash. New bathrooms beautifully tiled, one of which is equipped with a fully tiled shower. New 10 X 10 wooden deck off kitchen, perfect for year-round grilling! Nicely finished large family room in the basement. Don't miss out! Won't last!
